data.description: Experience the charm of Babcock Ranch living with this inviting Bismark villa floorplan by Lennar Homes, ready for immediate occupancy. Nestled in the desirable Trail's Edge neighborhood, this residence is designed for modern comfort and convenience.Step into a stylish kitchen adorned with stainless steel appliances and sleek granite countertops. The open living and dining area boasts contemporary laminate flooring, creating a welcoming atmosphere for both relaxation and entertainment. The tile accents add a touch of sophistication, elevating the overall aesthetic. A standout feature of this property is its expansive fenced backyard, one of the largest in all of Babcock Ranch. Enjoy the luxury of outdoor living and create cherished moments in this spacious and private outdoor retreat.Convenience is at your fingertips, with the property just minutes away from the Publix anchored shopping center at the main entrance to Babcock Ranch. This prime location ensures easy access to daily essentials and enhances the overall appeal of the neighborhood.
